Package: MultiAssaySpatialExperiment
Version: 0.9.0
Date: 2026-02-19
Title: Multi-Assay Experiment with Spatial Context
Description: Extends MultiAssayExperiment with spatial context elements
    (images, labels, points, shapes) for integrative analysis of spatially
    resolved multi-omics data. Supports coercion to and from
    SpatialExperiment, SpatialFeatureExperiment, and SpatialData.
